WEBVTT

00:01:28.360 --> 00:01:30.456
and when they leave

00:01:30.480 --> 00:01:33.800
they take along the story
and happiness with them.

00:01:34.760 --> 00:01:38.136
So when these people came to me,

00:01:38.160 --> 00:01:40.296
though TED has made it
easier for me today,

00:01:40.320 --> 00:01:44.376
by already casting a spell of happiness

00:01:44.400 --> 00:01:46.976
in which all of you are now trapped.

00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:48.440
Definitely.

00:01:48.440 --> 00:01:52.360
(Applause)

00:01:52.360 --> 00:01:57.696
These bubbles of happiness are
already bursting inside you,

00:01:57.720 --> 00:02:01.500
now my only job is to turn
them into cracking laughter.